{"tid":1231345,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：對唔住，我知錯了","createTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T12:56:01.000Z","uid":81783,"like":1,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9955d699000bd85a3ee70cc09eebf9d411e86de9","tid":1231345,"uid":81783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:41:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/16/P2019061600738.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201906%2F16%2FP2019061600738.htm&d=q0LkGBAelTJmoxhYCIypyfCGrV5sAEOTHy2vWGvapoA%3D&h=54e07227\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201906/16/P2019061600738.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府回應遊行<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n  就今日（六月十六日）的遊行，政府發言人作出以下回應：<br />\n <br />\n  過去兩個星期日，十分多市民透過遊行表達意見，政府明白市民遊行是出於對香港的關心和熱愛。<br />\n   <br />\n  對於市民一直以平和、理性方式表達意見，行政長官清楚聽到，並認同這正是香港作為一個文明、自由、開放、多元的社會，一直展現的互相尊重、和而不同的精神。政府重視和珍惜香港這些核心價值。<br />\n   <br />\n  考慮到社會有強烈不同的意見，政府已停止立法會大會對修訂《逃犯條例》的工作，希望藉此可讓社會盡快回復平靜和避免任何人受到傷害。<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">政府重申並無重啟程序的時間表</span></strong></span>。<br />\n   <br />\n  行政長官承認由於政府工作上的不足，令香港社會出現很大的矛盾和紛爭，令很多市民感到失望和痛心，<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行政長官為此向市民致歉，並承諾會以最有誠意、最謙卑的態度接受批評，加以改進，為廣大市民服務</span></span>。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年6月16日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間20時29分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><br />\n<br />\n但是死都唔撤回<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span>"},{"pid":"a0fce6d640a7ca62866d3a761627003f05010652","tid":1231345,"uid":160095,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:43:21.000Z","msg":"道歉講完 態度照舊 送終照過 不撤不散"},{"pid":"bb783a6ea2a380d690291c2560a0ec2ce2ba7d2d","tid":1231345,"uid":53156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:45:08.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">放左人未啊</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"695abb9388546ee3f910442453018a94282ab6bf","tid":1231345,"uid":50658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:45:24.000Z","msg":"7婆你道歉就天經地義，理所當然嘅<br />\n唔通要我同你講番多謝呀？"},{"pid":"f1a66c019d3f9d359b9ebe1795ad91be2a86c079","tid":1231345,"uid":17616,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:47:24.000Z","msg":"無時間表，我鍾意下星期再黎又得，下個月記返起再提又得"},{"pid":"b2273eb5b10216927cbd0a52dcd0f8bdf8edfbe5","tid":1231345,"uid":70691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"未作打算＝無撤回"},{"pid":"f447acbdfacd2054620f6dab456eb2fa5ea1c802","tid":1231345,"uid":144906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T12:56:01.000Z","msg":"準備姦你 道個歉 遲啲再姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}